<br>
Druids will now only be able to cast SoW. All other druid spells will be removed from the game.<br>
<br>
Bards will no longer be able to haste, slow, or buff resists. They will have to rely on their mana and damage absorb songs.<br>
<br>
A new spell in the Eye of Zomm series has been added.<br>
<br>
Wizards have been placed on a new melee damage table after they attain level 51.<br>
<br>
Wizard familiars will no longer take mana when they are killed. Instead, they will spit at you and call you a whore.<br>
<br>
Necromancers will be able to solo dragons.<br>
<br>
All clerics will be forced to specialize in Evocation. Any who don't comply will be severely punished by the Verant Interactive Secret Police. Also, wizards will be forced to specialize in Abjuration. <p><IMG SRC=http://www.tiannathomas.com/images/roliel3.gif>
